<SYNC Start=993459><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=995877><P Class=KRCC>
어떻게 된 겁니까?
<SYNC Start=996860><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=998953><P Class=KRCC>
